quran[195]{c,v,t}:
  46,1,"Haa, Miim"
  46,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  46,3,"Men tagiraali kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, si wanaa e goonga e lajala happaangal [fii mun]. Yeddu…ìe …ìen ko …óuurnii…ìe e ko …ìe rentiniraa kon"
  46,4,"Maaku: \"On yi'ii ko rewoton kon hara wanaa Allah, hollee lam ko …ói tagi e leydi ndin? Kaa hara hi…ói mari ge…ìal e [tagugol] kammuuli …óin? Awa addanee lam Deftere jippinaande ado ndee …óoo maa…óum batte ganndal, si wonii ko on goongu…ìe"
  46,5,"Ko hommbo …ìuri majjude, wa on rewoowo ko wanaa Allah, kon ko jaabotaako mo haa √ëalnde Darngal? Hara …óin [rewetee…ói] ko welsindii…ói e dewal majji"
  46,6,"Si yim…ìe …ìen moo…ìoyaama [ka Darngal], …ói wontanoyay …ìe ay…ìe, …ìe wona e yeddugol ko …ìe rewaynoo…ói kon"
  46,7,"Si Aayeeje Amen …ìanngu…óe …óen janngaama e ma…ì…ìe, yedunoo…ìe goonga …ìen tuma nde arnoo e ma…ì…ìe …ìen wi'a: \"∆äum ko mbilewu …ìanngu ngu"
  46,8,"Kaa …ìe wi'ay woni :\"O fefindi nde?\" Awa maaku: \"Si taw mi fefindi nde, awa doo on duncantaa lam huunde e [lepte] Allah …óen. Ko Kanko …ìuri anndude on, tuma nde jumpoton e mayre. O yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon. Ko Kanko woni Haforowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  46,9,"Maaku: \"Mi wonaa arano e Nulaa…ìe …ìen; mi anndaa kadi ko wa…óetee mi, maa ko wa…óete…óon. Mi jokkaa si wanaa ko wahayinaa kon e am; mi laataaki si wanaa jertinoowo …ìanngina"
  46,10,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, si tawii le konde iwrunde ka Allah, yeddu…óon …óum, seedotoo…óo e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'ila …ìen seedii e [sellugol] …óum, o gom…óini, onon kan towniti…óon...Pellet, Allah fewnataa yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  46,11,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen wi'ani gom…óim…ìe …ìen: \"Si tawno …óum ko mo∆¥∆¥ere, …ìen (waasu…ìe) adototaako men e mun\". Nde wonunoo …ìe fewnoraali nde, ma …ìe wi'u: \"Ndee ko fenaande nee…ìunde"
  46,12,"Hino aditiinde, Deftere Muusaa nden, …óowornde e yurmeende. Ndee …óoo kadi, ko Deftere goonginir- nde […óeya Defte] e …óemngal aarabu, fii yo jertinir (nde) too√±oo…ìe …ìen e wewlinirnde mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  46,13,"Pellet, wi'u…ìe …ìen: \"Ko Allah woni Joomi amen\", refti …ìe tabiti (e gom…óinal), kulol alanaa …ìen, wanaa kam…ìe sunoytoo"
  46,14,"Ko …ìen woni yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen duumotoo…ìe ton, njo…ìdi ko …ìe gollaynoo kon"
  46,15,"Men yamirii ne…ó…óanke on mo∆¥∆¥agol e jibim…ìe mo …ìen: Jiido makko soworike mo sa…óteende, o jibiniri mo kadi sa…óteende; soweede mo e enteede mo ko lebbi cappan…óe tati, haa ka o si o yottike sagatalaaku makku ngun o timminii duu…ìi cappan…óe nayi, o wi'a: \"Joomi, longinam yettugol neema Ma mo neeminir…óaa mi min e jibim…ìe lam, e nde mi gollata mo∆¥∆¥u…ói weltinay…óe Ma, mo∆¥∆¥inanaa lam geyngol am ngol. Mi tuubanii Ma, ko mi jeyaa…óo e jebbilii…ìe …ìen"
  46,16,"Ko …ìen woni …ìe Men ja…ìanta ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko …ìe golli, Men yawtana …ìe bon…ói ma…ì…ìe, (…ìe jeyaama) e yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen. ∆äum ko fodoore goonga nde …ìe fodanoo"
  46,17,"Kala non wi'an…óo jibim…ìe mo …ìen: \"Uf mo'on ! Kere on foday lam immintineede hara le gom…óii mofte yawtiino ado lam?\" Hara …ìen …ói…óo no faabtinora Allah [wiide mo]: \"Ee bone maa, Gom…óin ! Pellet, fodooree Allah nde ko goonga\". O wi'a: \"∆äum wonaali, si wanaa tinndi adinoo…ìe …ìen"
  46,18,"Ko …ìen woni …ìe Konngol ngol jojji e mun, (…ìe jeyaama) e mofte yawtunoo…óe ado ma…ì…ìe, immorde e jinna e yim…ìe. Pellet, …ìe laatino sooyu…ìe"
  46,19,"Hino woodani kala [fedde e ma…ì…ìe]: darjaaji e ko …ìe golli kon, fii no O hunnirana …ìe njo…ìdi golle ma…ì…ìe …óen; e hoore …ìe too√±etaake"
  46,20,"√ëalnde heefer…ìe …ìen wee…ìitoytee e Yiite ngen (…ìe wi'anee): \"On na…ìii mo∆¥∆¥i mon …óin ka nguurndam mon aduna, dakmitor…óon …ói. Hannde non, on yo…ìitirte lepte hoynooje, sabu ko townitorayno…óon kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko huuwirayno…óon kon faasiqaaku"
  46,21,"Janto fii musi…ó…ìe Aadi (Huudi) …ìen, nde o jertinirnoo yim…ìe makko …ìen aynde nden - gom…óii hari jertinooji yawtiino yeeso makko e …ìaawo makko - wonnde: \"Wata on rewu si wanaa Allah. Min mi…óo hulani on lepte √±alaande mawnde"
  46,22,"∆Åe wi'i: \"E a aru men fii yo a firliaa men e rewetee- …ói amen …óin? Awa addan men ko kammbiran…óaa men kon, si wonii ko a jeyaa…óo e goongu…ìe …ìen"
  46,23,"O maaki: \"Ganndal ngal ko ka Allah woni. Min mi yottinanay on tun woni, ko mi nulaa kon. Ko woni tun mi yi'ii ko on yim…ìe majjaa…ìe"
  46,24,"Nde …ìe yi'unoo ruulde honde wee…ìitii fewtiri ay…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe wi'i: \"Ndee ko duulere to…ìaynde e men\". Ko nden kan woni ! ko hawjirno…óon kon : ko henndu, ndu lepte muusu…óe woni e mun"
  46,25,"hindu muncira kala huunde, yamiroore Joomi mayru\". ∆Åe wa…ótini, tawi yi'etaake si wanaa ko…óooli ma…ì…ìe …óin. Ko wano nii Men yo…ìitirta yim…ìe bonnoo…ìe …ìen"
  46,26,"Gom…óii Men ye…óiino …ìe, e kon ko Men ye…óaali on e mun. Men wa…óani …ìe nan…óe, e gii…óe e …ìer…óe. Kono …óen nan…óe ma…ì…ìe, e gii…óe ma…ì…ìe e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe (fow) duncanaali …ìe go…ó…óum, tawde …ìe laatino yeddoo…ìe Aayeeje Allah …óen. Ko …ìe jalkitaynoo kon jippii e ma…ì…ìe"
  46,27,"Gom…óii Men halkiino ca'e wonunoo…ìe sera mon; Men firlitiri Aayeeje …óen, belajo'o …ìe ruttoto"
  46,28,"Ko ha…óno …óin …ói …ìe jogitornoo rewetee…ói …ìa…ótinor…ói gaanin Allah, faaboo …ìe? Tigi on, …óin majjirii …ìe; ko …óum wonunoo fenaande ma…ì…ìe e ko …ìe fefindotonoo"
  46,29,"Janto tuma nde Men imminnoo fedde jinna e maa…óa, hi…ói he…óoo Alqur'aana. Nde …ói tawanoo …óum, …ói wi'i: \"He…óee\"...Nde [janngin kin] timmunoo, …ói huccitiri ka yim…ìe majji, jeertinooji"
  46,30,"∆äi wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu amen, men nanii Deftere jippinaande …ìaawo Muusaa, goonginnde …óen adii…óe nde. Hinde fewna e goonga e laawol focciingol"
  46,31,"Ko ono yo mbatu amen, nootee noddoowo e Allah on, gom…óinon mo. [Ontuma] O haforanay on junuubimon …óin, O da…ónda on lepte muusu…óe"
  46,32,"Kala mo nootaake noddoowo e Allah on, o wonaa laawotoo…óo ka leydi, o alaa kadi gi…óo gaanin Makko. Ko …ìen woni e nder majjere …ìanngunde"
  46,33,"E …ìee yi'aali wonnde ko Allah tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, O ronkiraali tagugol …ói, wonnde ko O ha…ótan…óo wuurnitugol maay…ìe …ìen? Ko non woniri. Pellet, ko O ha…ótan…óo kala huunde"
  46,34,"√ëalnde heefer…ìe …ìen wee…ìitoytee e Yiite ngen, […ìe wi'anee]: \"Wanaa goonga nii?\" ∆Åe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri! Men woondirii Joomi amen!\". O Daala : \"Awa mee…óiree non lepte …óen, sabu kon ko yeddirayno…óon"
  46,35,"Mu√±√±or mu√±al joomiraa…ìe pellital …ìen ka Nulaa…ìe; wata a hawjan …ìe. √ëalnde …ìe yi'oyta ko …ìe kammbiranaa kon, …ìe wa'oyay wa si …ìe √±ii…ìaano [ka leydi] si wanaa dumunna-hun √±alorma. ∆äun ko yottinal. Ko hom…ìe halketee si wanaa yim…ìe faasiqii…ìe …ìen"
  47,1,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe …ìe falii laawol Allah ngol, O bonnii golle ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,2,"Gom…óim…ìe …ìen …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, …ìe gom…óini ko jippinaa kon e Muhammad - on goonga immor…óo e Joomi ma…ì…ìe - O yawtanii …ìe bon…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin, O mo∆¥∆¥inii fiyaaku ma…ì…ìe on"
  47,3,"Ko wa…ói …óum, ko tawde yeddu…ìe …ìen jokkii meere nden, gom…óim…ìe …ìen kan jokki goonga kan immorde e Joomi ma…ì…ìe on. Ko wano nii Allah piyiranta yim…ìe …ìen mise ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,4,"Si on arii hawrude e yeddu…ìe …ìen (ka hare), ko soppugol daa…óe …óen. Haa si on …óu…ó…óinii warugol …ìe, ha…ì…ìon koy…óe …óen. Ko si on mo∆¥∆¥oray e ma…ì…ìe accitugol …ìe …ìaawo …óum, maa si ko soktiigu, haa hare nden wallina jogaaji mayre. Ko non √±aawiraa, si Allah no muuyunoo, O wallitotono on e ma…ì…ìe, ko woni tun, ko no O jarribora yoga mon e dow yoga. Waraa…ìe fii Allah …ìen, pellet, O yeebataa golle ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,5,"Arma O fewna …ìe, O mo∆¥∆¥ina fiyaaku ma…ì…ìe"
  47,6,"O naadoya …ìe Aljanna, mo O anndini …ìe fii mun"
  47,7,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe, si on wonii walloo…ìe fii Allah, O wallay on, O tabintina teppe mon …óen"
  47,8,"Yeddu…ìe …ìee kan, halkaare woodanii …ìe, O majjinii kadi golle ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,9,"∆äum le ko tawde …ìe a√±ii ko Allah jippini kon, O bonni golle ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,10,"E …ìee yiilaaki e leydi ndin, …ìe teskoo ko honno battane adinoo…ìe …ìen wa'unoo? Allah halkuno fii ma…ì…ìe. sugu mum kadi hino woodani yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  47,11,"Ko wa…ói …óum, ko tawde ko Allah woni gi…óo gom…óim…ìe …ìen; hara non yeddu…ìe …ìen, gi…óo (woo) alanaa …ìe"
  47,12,"Pellet, Allah naadoyay gom…óim…ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói …ìen, Aljannaaji …ói can…ói ilata ley (ku…ìeeje) majje. Yeddu…ìe …ìen kan, hi…ìe dakmitoo, …ìe √±aamira wano neemoraa…ói …óin √±aamirta; hara non ko Yiite ngen woni jaa∆¥orde ma…ì…ìe. @Corrected"
  47,13,"∆äuu…óii e ca'e, …ìurnoo…ìe tii…óude cemmbe, e dii ndeen saare maa ra…óiinde ma, …ìe Men halki, ballo alanaa …ìe"
  47,14,"Kere ko on won…óo e …ìanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mun, wa'i wa …ìen cu…óinanaa…ìe kuu…óe mun bon…óe …óen, …ìe jokki mbelee…óe ma…ì…ìe"
  47,15,"Ko woni sifa Aljanna fodaa…óo on gom…óu…ìe …ìen: ina toon can…ói ndiyam …ói dakamme mun waylaaki, e can…ói …ìira …ói waylataa dakamme mun, e can…ói konnjam welay…óam yaroo…ìe, e can…ói njuuri la…ì…ìinaandi. Hino woodani …ìe kadi ton: kala dim…ìe, e haforaneede immorde e Joomi ma…ì…ìe. [∆Åen wa'oyay] wa luttinoyteee…ìe …ìen ka Yiite, …ìe yarnee ndiyam fatay…óam, …óam ta∆¥a tetekki ma…ì…ìe …óin"
  47,16,"Hino e ma…ì…ìe he…óitotoo…ìe ma. Kono ko haa si …ìe yaltii ka maa…óa, …ìe wi'ana okkaa…ìe ganndal …ìen: \"Ko hon…óum dee, o wi'unoo naanen?\" Ko …ìen woni …ìe Allah noti e …ìer…óe mun …óen, …ìe jokki mbelee…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,17,"Feewu…ìe …ìen kan, O …ìeydu …ìe peewal O okki…ìe gom…óal ma…ì…ìe"
  47,18,"Hara …ìee no habbii si wanaa Darngal ngal nde ardata …ìe e juhal? Gom…óii le maandeeji maggal arii. Ko honno …ìe waajitoroyta, si ngal ardanii …ìe (juhal)"
  47,19,"Awa anndu pellet, rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Allah, insinano…óaa junuubi maa …óin, e gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe …ìen. Allah no anndi √±allirde mon e hiirirde mon"
  47,20,"Gom…óim…ìe …ìen hino wi'a: \"Hara nun cortewol (hare) jippotono!\" Si tawii le cortewol √±e√±aangol jippinaama, fii hare jantaama e maggol, a tinay …ìen …ìe √±awu woni e …ìer…óe mun hino ndaare, ndaar…óe mo maayde fa…ó…óini. Ko haanannoo …ìe"
  47,21,"ko …óoftagol e konngol mo∆¥∆¥ol. Si fiyaaku on fellitii, hara nun …ìe gom…óinno Allah, ko …óum …ìuraynoo mo∆¥∆¥annde …ìe"
  47,22,"E on tam∆¥inaaki, si wonii on …óuurnike, nde bonnoton e leydi ndin, ta∆¥on en…óamaaji mon"
  47,23,"Ko …ìen woni …ìe Allah hu…ói …ìen, O faa…óini …ìe, O wumini gii…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,24,"E …ìee tasktaako Alqur'aana, kaa ko sokir…óe woni woni e …ìer…óe mum en"
  47,25,"Pellet, …ìen ruttor…ìe …ìabbe mun …ìaawo nde peewal ngal …ìanngannoo …ìe, ko seytaane cu…óinani …ìe, o hodi …ìe"
  47,26,"Ko tawde …ìe wi'anii …ìen a√±u…ìe ko Allah jippini kon: \"Men …óoftoto on e yoga e piiji\". Allah non no anndi gunndooji ma…ì…ìe …óin"
  47,27,"Ko honno (…ìee wa'oyta) tuma nde Malaa'ika'en timmini fii ma…ì…ìe, hara hi…ìe bantoo geece ma…ì…ìe e dote ma…ì…ìe"
  47,28,"Ko tawde ko …ìe jokkii ko tikkinta Allah, …ìe a√±ii welay…ói Mo …óin, O bonni fii golle ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,29,Kaa …ìen …ìe √±awu woni e …ìer…óe mun sikuu wonnde Allah yaltintaa ngaynguuji ma…ì…ìe
  47,30,"Sinno Men haajuno, Men holleteno …ìe. Anndiraa …ìe maandeeji ma…ì…ìe …óin; ko pellet, a anndirayno …ìe ka konngol welngol. Allah non hino anndi golle mon …óen"
  47,31,"Ma Men jarribo on, haa Men annda tii…ónii…ìe …ìen e mon, e mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen. Men jarriboo kadi kabaruuji mon"
  47,32,"Pellet, yeddu…ìe …ìen …ìe faddi laawol Allah ngol, …ìe lunndii Nulaa…óo on …ìaawo nde peewal ngal …ìanngannde …ìe, …ìen lorrataa Allah hay huunde. Ma O bonnu fii golle ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,33,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe! ∆äoftee Allah, …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on, wata on bonnu golle mon …óen"
  47,34,"Pellet, …ìen yeddu…ìe …ìe sakkii e laawol Allah ngol, hooti …ìe maayi ko …ìe heefer…ìe, Allah haforanoytaa …ìe"
  47,35,"Wata on lo'inkino, noddon e beldal, ko onon woni foolu…ìe …ìen, Allah no wonndi e mon, O ustantaa on njo…ìdi golle mon …óen"
  47,36,"Anndee nguurndam aduna ko fijindaaru e mbelee…óe tan; hara le si on gom…óiii, on hulii [Allah], O ye…óay on njo…ìdi mon ndin, o lamndotaako on jawle mon …óen"
  47,37,"Si O aru lamndaade on fii majje, haa O du√±ii on (e mun), wuddon, O fe√±√±ina non konnaagu mon ngun"
  47,38,"Hey mon onon …óoo, hi…óo noddee e nafqugol fii laawol Allah ngol. Hino e mo'on wudday…ìe. Kala non wuddu…óo, haray ko hoore-makko o wuddani. Ko Allah woni Galo On, onon won…óon waasu…ìe …ìen. Si on huccii, O wa…ótitira on wo…ó…ìe goo, hara non …ìen wa'ataa wano mon"
  48,1,Men udditanii ma uddital …ìanngungal
  48,2,"fii no Allah yawtirani kon ko ardin…óaa e junuubi, e ko sakkitii, e fii no O timminira neema Makko on e maa…óa, O fewne e laawol foocciingol"
  48,3,e no Allah wallire ballal tii…óungal
  48,4,"Ko Kanko woni jippin…óo dee∆¥ere nden e …ìer…óe gom…óim…ìe …ìen, fii no …ìe …ìeydora gom…óinal e dow gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe ngal. Ko Allah woodani koneeli kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin; Allah siforii wonnde Anndu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  48,5,"e fii no O naadira gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, Aljannaaji …ói can…ói ilata ley mun, ko …ì…óe duumotoo…ìe e majji, e no O montira-na…ìe ban…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin. ∆äum wonii ka Allah, malal mawnungal. @Corrected"
  48,6,"E no O leptira naafiqii…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e naafiqii…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e sirkoo…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e sirkoo…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, sikkoo…ìe Allah sikke bon…óe. Yiiloonde bon…ói ngonii e dow ma…ì…ìe. Allah tikkanii…ìe kadi, O hu…óii …ìe, O hebilanii …ìe Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  48,7,"Ko Allah woodani konuuji kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Allah siforii wonnde Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  48,8,"Men nulirii ma seedotoo…óo, wewlinoowo, e jertinoowo"
  48,9,"fii no gom…óiniron Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, mawninon mo, teddinon mo, subbunhinano…óon Mo bimmbi e kiikii…óe"
  48,10,"Pellet, …ìen won…ìe ahodude e maa…óa, anndu ko Allah …ìe woni e ahodude. Junngo Allah ngon no senngo dow juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen. Kala non firtu…óo, haray ko hoore makko o firtani; kala kadi hunnu…óo ko o ahodi kon e Allah, aray nde O okkata mo njo…ìdi mawnundi"
  48,11,"Aray nde tultu…ìe jeyaa…ìe e yim…ìe ladde …ìen wi'ane: \"Jawle amen …óen e …ìeynguureeji amen …óin sokolinii men. Insinano men\". Hi…ìe wowlira …óem…óe ma…ì…ìe, ko alaa e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe. Maaku: \"Ko hommbo waawani on ka Allah, si O faandanike on lorra maa hara O faandani on nafa? Wurin Allah siforiino wonnde Humpitii…óo ko gollayno…óon kon"
  48,12,"Wurin on sukkuno Nulaa…óo on e gom…óim…ìe …ìen artataano fes ka …ìeynguureeji ma…ì…ìe. ∆äum cu…óinaa e …ìer…óe mon; sikku…óon sikke bon…óe, laati…óon yim…ìe halkaa…ìe"
  48,13,"Kala dee mo gom…óinaali Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, haray Me…óen heblani yeddu…ìe …ìen (Yiite) dulbaynge"
  48,14,"Ko Allah heeranii laamagol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo haforana mo O muuyani, O lepta mo O muuyani. Allah siforii wonnde Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  48,15,"Aray nde luttu…ìe …ìen wi'a, tuma fokkitanoyton henndagol konu-hoyri ndin: \"Accee men jokka on\". Hi…ìe faalaa wa…ótitugol daalol Allah ngol. Maaku: \"On jokkataa men fes. Ko wano mon nii Allah daalirnoo oya tuma\". Ma …ìe wi'u: \"On a√±anay men tun woni\". Tigi on, …ìe faamataano si wanaa see…óa"
  48,16,"Maakan tultu…ìe …ìen e yim…ìe ladde …ìen: \"Arma nde noddete…óon e yim…ìe joomiraa…ìe doole tii…óu…ìe. Ho…ìon …ìe maa…óum …ìe silma. Si on …óoftike, Allah okkay on mbarjaari mo∆¥∆¥undi; si on huccitirii no huccitirno…óon oya tuma, O leptira lepte muusu…óe"
  48,17,"Bakkaatu fawaaki e hoore …ìun…óo on, wanaa e la∆¥oowo on wanaa kadi e nawnu…óon bakkaatu fawii. Kala …óoftii…óo Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, O naadoyay mo Aljannaaji …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley mun. Kala kadi …óuurnii…óo, O leptiray mo lepte muusu…óe"
  48,18,"Gom…óii Allah welano gom…óim…ìe …ìen, tuma …ìe ahondiraynoo e maa…óa ka ley lekki kin. O anndi ko woni kon ka …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe, O jippini dee∆¥ere nden e ma…ì…ìe, O warjorii…ìe uddital …ìadiingal"
  48,19,"e konu-heyri …óuu…óundi ndi …ìe henndotoo. Allah siforii wonnde Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  48,20,"Allah fodii on konu-heyri …óuu…óundi ndi henndoto…óon, O yaccinani on ndii …óoo, O suri juu…óe yim…ìe …ìen e mo'on, fii yo wonu maande wonannde gom…óim…ìe …ìen, O fewnira on laawol focciingol"
  48,21,"E wonndi goo ndi on ha…ótanaali taho, Allah kan no hu…ìindii ndi. Allah siforii wonnde ha…ótan…óo kala huunde"
  48,22,"Hay si yeddu…ìe …ìen ha…ìiino on, …ìe huccintinayno …ìabbe ma…ì…ìe …óen, refti …ìe he…ìataano gi…óo wanaa ballao"
  48,23,"∆äum ko sunna Alla fe∆¥∆¥unoo…óo ko adii. A he…ìantaa laawol Alla ngol, mbattiigu"
  48,24,"Ko Kanko woni suran…óo on juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen e mo'on, e suru…óo juu…óe mon …óen e ma…ì…ìe, ka aynde Makka, …ìaawo O foolnude on e ma…ì…ìe. Allah siforii wonnde Reenu…óo ko golloton kon"
  48,25,"Ko …ìen woni ko yeddi, …ìe faddii on e Juurlirde Hormorde nden, […ìe ha…ói] neldaari ndin nde ndi yottotoo nokku mayri. Si wanaano sabu wor…ìe gom…óim…ìe e rew…ìe gom…óim…ìe …ìe on anndataano haa ha…ìon …ìe, bakkaatu he…ìa on e fee ma…ì…ìe, ko aldaa e anndugol... fii yo Allah naadu e yurmeende Makko nden, on mo O muuyani. Si …ìe senndondir-no [e gom…óim…ìe …ìen], ko pellet, Men leptirayno yeddu…ìe …ìen e ma…ì…ìe, lepte muusu…óe"
  48,26,"Tuma nde …ìeya yeddu…ìe wa…óunoo ka …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe jinngo, jinngo majjiyanke...Allah jippini dee∆¥ere Makko nden e dow Nulaa…óo Makko on e gom…óim…ìe …ìen, O fawi …ìe konngol gom…óal, …ìe woni …ìur…ìe jojjude e hanndude e maggol. Allah siforii Anndugol kala huunde"
  48,27,"Gom…óii Allah goonginiranii Nulaa…óo Makko on, koy…óol ngol e hoore goonga : Ko maa naaton e juulirde Hormorde nden si Allah muuyii, hara ko on hoolii…ìe, femmbu…ìe ko*e mon maa …óuytu…ìe (cukuli), on hulataa. Himo anndi ko on anndaa. O wa…ói ko wanaa ngol (naatugol Makko) …óon, uddital …ìadiingal"
  48,28,"Ko Kanko woni Nulir…óo Nulaa…óo Makko on peewal e diina goonga, fii yo o fawaka ka e hoore kala diina. Allah yonii seedee"
  48,29,"Muhammdu ko Nulaa…óo Allah. Wonndu…ìe e makko …ìen ko √±aa…óu…ìe e yeddu…ìe …ìen, yurmondir…ìe hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. A yi'ay …ìe hi…ìe ru∆¥∆¥a, hi…ìe sujja, hi…ìe …óa…ì…ìira Allah …ìural e welayee. Maandeeji ma…ì…ìe …óin no ka geece ma…ì…ìe batte sujjugol ngol. Ko …óum woni ko …ìe siforaa ka Tawreeta. No …ìe siforaa ka Linjiila kan, ko wano remuru yaltingu pu…ói mayru, ngu …ìanngini …ói, …ói tekki, …ói fotondiri e binndeeje majji, hara …óum no haawna remoo…ìe, fii no [Allah] tikkinira …ìe yeddu…ìe …ìen. Allah fodii e ma…ì…ìe …ìen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói …óin, haforanal e njo…ìdi mawnundi"
  49,1,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! wata on adito yeeso Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on. Hulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  49,2,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! wata on towu sowtooji mon e hoore sowto Annabaajo on, wata on ewnor mo kadi konngol, wano no yoga mon ewnorta yoga, sakko golle mon …óen bonata, hara on so'aa-anndude"
  49,3,"Pellet, …ìen joltinoo…ìe sowtooji ma…ì…ìe …óin ka Nulaa…óo Allah on, ko …ìen woni …ìe Alla jarabii …ìer…óe mun …óen gom…óal. Hino woodani …ìe haforanal e njo…ìdi mawndi"
  49,4,"Pellet, …ìen …ìe no noddire ka …ìaawo cuu…ói, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, wanaa haqqiloo…ìe"
  49,5,"Sinno …ìe mu√±√±ino haa yaltaa e ma…ì…ìe, ko …óum …ìuraynoo mo∆¥∆¥annde …ìe. Allah ko Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  49,6,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! Si faasiqiijo ardanii on e kumpital, tefee fii wata on he…ìor e yim…ìe sabu majjeede, wonton ninsu…ìe e kon ko wa…óu…óon"
  49,7,"Anndee wonnde Nulaa…óo Allah on hino hakkunde mon. Si o tewtino on e ko …óuu…ói e fiyakuuji, on tampayno. Kono Allah yi…óini on gom…óinal, O cu…óini ngal e …ìer…óe mon; O a√±ini on keeferaaku, e faasiqaaku e geddi. Ko …ìen woni feewu…ìe …ìen"
  49,8,"…óum ko …ìural immorde ka Allah e neema. Allah ko Anndu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  49,9,"Si feddeeji …ói…ói e gom…óim…ìe …ìen ha…ìii, mo∆¥∆¥intinee hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Si fedde goo bewii e hoore ndeya, ko ha…ìugol wonnde e bewude nden, haa nde ruttoo e yamiroore Allah nden. Si nde ruttike, mo∆¥∆¥intiniree hakkunde ma…ì…ìe nun…óal. Nun…óee, tawde pellet, Allah no yi…ói nun…óoo…ìe …ìen"
  49,10,"Anndee gom…óim…ìe …ìen ko jeydu…ìe. Haray mo∆¥∆¥inee hakkunde jeydal mon ngal, hulon Allah, belajo'o on yurminte"
  49,11,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! Wata yim…ìe jalnor yim…ìe : hino gasa hara …ìen (jalaa…ìe) hino …ìuri …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ude. Wanaa rew…ìe woni ko jalnorta rew…ìe : hino gasa hara …ìen no …ìuri …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ude. Wata on aybidnir ko'e-mon, wata on bugondir jammooje (bon…óe). Innde faasiqaaku nden bonii …ìaawo nde gom…óinal nden. Kala mo tuubaali, ko …ìen woni too√±u…ìe …ìen"
  49,12,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! Wo…ó…óitee e ko …óuu…ói e sikke. Pellet, yoga e sikke ko bakkaatu. Wata on wi…óondir, wata yoga mon √±o'u yoga. Hara gooto e mo'on yi…óay √±aamugol teewu musi…ó…óo mun maay…óo? Hi…óon a√±i …óum. Hulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Ja…ìoowo tuubuubuyee, Hinnotoo…óo"
  49,13,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe ! Men tagiriii on immorde e gorel e deyel, Men wa…óiri on le∆¥∆¥i e gori, fii yo on anndindir. Pellet, …ìur…ìe teddude e mon …ìen ka Allah, ko …ìur…ìe gom…óude …ìen e mon. Pellet, Allah ko Anndu…óo, Humpitii…óo"
  49,14,"Yim…ìe ladde …ìen wi'i: \"Men gom…óinii\". Maaku: \"On gom…óinaali taho. Wi'ee kan : Men silmii. Gom…óinal ngal naataali taho ka …ìer…óe mon. Si on …óoftike Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, O …óuytantaa on huunde e golle mon …óen\". Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  49,15,"Gom…óim…ìe (tigi) …ìen, ko …ìen gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, refti …ìe sikkitaaki, …ìe tii…ónori kadi jawle e pittaali ma…ì…ìe …óin fii laawol Allah ngol. Ko …ìen woni goongu…ìe …ìen"
  49,16,"Maaku: \"Kere on anndinay Allah diina mon kan, hara non Allah no anndi kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi?\" Allah ko Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  49,17,"Hi…ìe waj Ma fii …ìe silmii. Maaku: \"Wata on wajitam silmugol mon. Si ko woni, ko Allah wajitata on fii O fewnirii on e gom…óinal, si wonii ko on goongu…ìe"
  49,18,"Pellet, Allah no anndi wirnii…ói kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Allah ko Reenu…óo ko golloton kon"
  50,1,Qaaf. Mi woondirii Alqur'aanaare teddunde nden
  50,2,"Si ko woni, …ìe ≈ãal…óu ko tawi kon jertinoowo arii …ìe iw…óo e ma…ì…ìe ; heefer…ìe …ìen wi'i: \"∆äum …óoo ko huunde haawniinde"
  50,3,"Kere si men maayii, men wontii mbulmbuldi...? ∆äum …óon ko ruttitagol wo…ó…óungol non"
  50,4,Gom…óii Me…óen anndi ko leydi ndin √±aamata kon e ma…ì…ìe ; hino ka Amen gaa deftere reenunde
  50,5,"Si ko woni, …ìe fennu goonga kan tuma nde ka arunoo e ma…ì…ìe, hi…ìe e nder fiyaaku jil…ìu…óo"
  50,6,"E …ìee ndaaraali kammu ngun dow ma…ì…ìe, ko honno Men mahiri ngun Men cu…óini ngu ; hara per…ói alanaa ngu"
  50,7,"Leydi ndin kadi, Men weerti ndi Men werlii e mayri pelle, Men fu…óini e mayri kala nooneeji [pu…ói] woo…óu…ói"
  50,8,fii tasakuyee e waaju wonannde kala jeyaa…óo ruttotoo…óo
  50,9,"Men jippini kadi ndiyam barkinaa…óam ummaade ka kammu, Men fu…óiniri …óam gese e gabbe so√±etee…óe"
  50,10,e le…ó…óe tamaro juutu…óe wondu…óe e piindi fawondirndi
  50,11,ko arsike jeyaa…ìe …ìen. Men wuurnitiri …óam kadi leydi yoorundi. Awa ko non woni fii ummital ngal
  50,12,"Ado ma…ì…ìe, yim…ìe nuuhu …ìen, e yim…ìe ∆Åunndu …ìen e Samuuda'en [fow] fennuno"
  50,13,"e 'Aadi'en, e Fir'awna e musi…ó…ìe Luutu …ìen"
  50,14,"e yim…ìe fitaare nden, e yim…ìe Tubba' …ìen. Kala ma…ì…ìe fennuno Nulaa…ìe …ìen, kammbaa Am on jojji"
  50,15,"Kere Men ronkuno fii tagu aranu ngun? Ko woni kam…ìe, hi…ìe e ji…ìaare fii tagiteede laawol kesol"
  50,16,"Gom…óii Men tagii ne…ó…óanke on, Me…óen anndi ko wonkii makko kin sowinsinirta mo. Ko Menen …ìuri …ìadaade mo e dii …óa…óol (makko) daande ngol"
  50,17,"tuma nde ja…ì…ìoytoo…ìe …ìen …ói…óo ja…ì…ìoroytoo [golle makko …óen] √±aamo e nano, hara hi…ìe joo…óii"
  50,18,"O wowlataa konngol, si wanaa hino takko makko winndoowo tawaa…óo"
  50,19,"∆äe…ó…óere maayde nden ardi e goonga : \"Ko …óum wonunoo ko dogayno…óaa"
  50,20,Wuttee ka alaandu ; ko nden woni √ëalaande kammbaa nden
  50,21,"Wonkii kala ara, hara hiki wonndi e soggoowo e seedotoo…óo"
  50,22,Gom…óii a laatinoke welsindii…óo e ndee. Men hunci wirngallo maa ngon kisan; gite maa …óen hannde ko see…ìu…óe
  50,23,"Wonndii…óo makko on wi'a: \"Ko …óum …óoo woni ka am …óoo, maandinaa-…óum"
  50,24,"Bugee ka Jahannama onon …ói…óo, kala yeddu…óo canndallo"
  50,25,"ha…óoowo mo∆¥∆¥ere, jaggitoowo, sikkitii…óo"
  50,26,on wa…óidu…óo e Allah rewetee…óo goo. Bugee mo ka nder lepte sa…ótu…óe
  50,27,"Cinndadiijo makko (seytaane) on wi'i: \"Joomi amen, mi bewinaali oo; si ko woni, ko e majjere wo…ó…óunde o wonunoo e mun"
  50,28,"[Allah] daala : \"Wata on yeddondir ka Am …óoo ! Nde tawnoo Mi ardiniino e mon kammbaa"
  50,29,Konngol wa…ótitetaake ka Am …óoo ; Mi siforaa kadi too√±oowo jeyaa…ìe …ìen
  50,30,"√ëalnde Men wi'anoyta Jahannama on : \"E a heewii?\" Nge wi'a: \"Ko …ìeydee hino woodi"
  50,31,"Aljanna on …ìa…ótinanee gom…óu…ìe …ìen, hara wanaa ka wo…ó…ói"
  50,32,"Ko …óum …óoo woni ko foda…óon, wonannde kala ruttii…óo [e Joomi mun] reenii…óo"
  50,33,"on hulu…óo Jom Hinaranke On ka wirnii, o ardi e …ìernde laa…ìunde"
  50,34,"Naatiree mo e jam\". Ko nden woni √±alaande luttaynde nden"
  50,35,"Hino woodani …ìe ton kala ko …ìe faaletee, hara kadi …ìeydaari hino ka Amen"
  50,36,"∆äuu…óii e gire …óen Men halki ado ma…ì…ìe, ko …ìen …ìurnoo…ìe doole, …ìen wanngorii e leydi ndin, ndaarugol taw si …ìe he…ìay laaworde"
  50,37,"Pellet, wonii e …óum, waaju wonannde kala jom …ìernde, maa tu…óu…óo noppi hara ko tawaa…óo"
  50,38,"Gom…óii Men tagii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, nder bal…óe jeegoo, tampere woo he…ìaali Men. @Corrected"
  50,39,"Mu√±√±o e ko …ìe wowlata kon, subbunhinano…óaa Joomi maa ado pu…óal naange ngen e ado mutal ngal"
  50,40,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinano…óaa Mo e ka battane [jul…óe] farlaa…óe"
  50,41,"He…óo, √±alnde noddoowo on noddoyta e nokkuure …ìadiinde"
  50,42,"√±alnde …ìe naniroyta haacaango ngon e hoore goonga. Ko nden woni √ëalnnde yaltugol ngol [ka genaale]"
  50,43,"Pellet, ko Menen wuurnata Men wara, ko ka Amen kadi woni ruttorde nden"
  50,44,"√ëalnde leydi ndin seekotoo […ìe yaltira] he√±agol; ko nde woni moo…ìirde newaniinde Men"
  50,45,"Ko Menen …ìuri anndude ko …ìe wowlata kon. A wonaa dooloowo…ìe. Haray waajor Alqur'aanaare nden, kala huloowo kammbaa An on"
  51,1,Mi woondirii keneeli jaroray…ói (leydi) jaragol
  51,2,Mi woondirii duule ronndotoo…óe to…ìo tii…óngo
